name: Duet
description:
This edition of 9 is the very first Electric Catnip NFT.

I chose “Duet” to be my first NFT because it is a visual expression of my memories of the magical moments in the early days of love, when there seem to be infinite possibilities.

When I uploaded “Duet” to GIPHY in 2018, I never imagined that it would be used in digital expressions of love over 60 MILLION times. It’s amazing to know that people use it every day to send a kiss in chat, in posts, and stories.

“Duet” captures the sweet trepidation and glowing hopefulness in the moments before a first kiss. Feel the purring visuals, see the world glow. This electric moment can be played as a seamless loop to last forever.

***

This NFT drop is the premiere of the 4K resolution version of “Duet”, the GIPHY original was 1080p.
